This video captures the raw, vibrant energy of the duo, showcasing the magic they created during that golden era. Get ready to relive the nostalgia and witness the iconic song in a whole new light. Speed Records proudly presents the Original Full Video Song of 'Angreji Beat' ‚Äì a treasure unlocked after 13 years!

snippet.title: Making of a Breaking News üì∞ | Baat Ka Batangad - E03 | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In this Video, we dive into the wild world of Indian news media, where every small issue becomes "Breaking News," and sensationalism takes center stage. Watch as reporters compete to turn the most trivial stories into national debates, completely ignoring real issues that actually matter.
From exaggerated headlines to over-the-top anchors and debates that lead nowhere, this sketch hilariously captures how news channels have turned into content creators battling for TRPs and views. With drama, absurdity, and non-stop laughter, Khabron Ka Bazaar holds up a mirror to the current state of news media.

snippet.title: Make DOLLAR great again - Trump's message to PM Modi | Abhi and Niyu

From economic policies to international diplomacy, we‚Äôll break down how Trump plans to counter this growing trend and protect the dollar's position as the world‚Äôs leading reserve currency. What does this mean for the global economy? How will it affect your everyday life? We‚Äôll discuss the potential impact on trade, inflation, and the U.S. economy at large.

Watch until the end for insights into how this plan could shape the future of global finance and what role you can play in understanding these crucial shifts.
